response.original_title: Stand UP, Speak OUT: Reproductive Rights - Birth Control
response.overview: Women talk about the consequences of having or not having access to effective birth control. Over the past 50 years, medical and social advances have given women more control over their reproductive health.
response.tagline: Women talk about the consequences of having or not having effective birth control.
